      "side": 1,
      "message": "Orthogonal to this (don\u0027t need to worry about it for this CL), but I previously realized the Kind vs. NumberKind distinction isn\u0027t helping us much? They\u0027re strictly mutually exclusive at this point - either kScalar (and then NumberKind fully determines the actual kind), or non-numeric, where NumberKind is ignored. Seems like we could collapse to a single enum?",
